{"tid":1724113,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和勇不分？","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:57:23.000Z","uid":10779,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1289224e17c4f876cf7afb898f1264e20888f585","tid":1724113,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話和勇不分？<br />\n依家又勇屌和唔出黎 憑咩俾意見出聲明<br />\n和又屌勇裝修傷及無辜 喺大學做大台<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動唔同人有唔同能力唔同角色<br />\n唔計得把口班撚樣啦<br />\n但唔係個個都做到勇武<br />\n做和理非都可以做好多野<br />\n亦都好多和理非好出力<br />\n做到嘅都會做<br />\n<br />\n唔好再分和勇ok?<br />\n唔好再屌唔出黎衝嘅人<br />\n成場運動所有嘢係自願<br />\n和同勇 缺一不可 <br />\n再分落去 呢場運動會輸<br />\n唔好重複五年前嘅錯<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得一開始講嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n大家係自己能力範圍內做好自己本分<br />\n同埋自律 <br />\n唔好有權力喺手就做大台 (eg幾間大學面對嘅問題)<br />\nOk? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[b]<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n香港人 報仇</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"476f07a621af791c29b7f8db39afaa8de6839c28","tid":1724113,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rehV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rehV1.jpg&h=1f4d5a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0362cb8dddeac3eb4f6ae824dd0037a5a6ee14","tid":1724113,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb92b918c6fe1afa0154b16517f9042e7ecc71c4","tid":1724113,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c48f0ce571125de7e26eefd009526e53d234ec","tid":1724113,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"大家都係自己人<br />\n<br />\n只有改善空間 冇割席空間<br />\n<br />\n學下黑警睇下咩叫打頭都唔